<h2 id="student-positions">Student positions</h2>

<p>The Ben-David lab is recruiting students at all levels. Our work combines bench work with the amazing <em>C. elegans</em> model with advanced computational genomic analyses. If this combination appeals to you and it’s something you want to learn, <a href="mailto: eyal.bendavid@mail.huji.ac.il.">apply here</a></p>

